# Personal theses — keep your real ones private (any variant: theses_old.md,
# "theses backup.md", ...). Commit theses.example.md instead.
theses*.md
!theses.example.md

# Generated reports may contain personal opinions / position-revealing content.
reports/

# Local execution logs.
logs/

